Class TestFromClientSideWithCoprocessor

java.lang.Object
org.apache.hadoop.hbase.client.FromClientSideBase

org.apache.hadoop.hbase.client.TestFromClientSideWithCoprocessor
public class TestFromClientSideWithCoprocessor extends TestFromClientSide
Test all client operations with a coprocessor that just implements the default flush/compact/scan policy.

Base class was split into three so this class got split into three. See below for other parts.
